                            </div>
                            <p>Every freelancer is rigorously verified so you work only with the best professionals in the industry.</p>
                        </div><!-- End Tab 2 Content -->
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="about-2-tab3">
                            <p class="fst-italic">Our vision is to revolutionize the freelance market by creating a dynamic, global community where opportunities and talents seamlessly connect.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
                                <i class="bi bi-check2"></i>
